description: Seafire AB engages in the acquisition and investment of small to medium sized companies. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 20 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-11-16. Its portfolio comprises such subsidiaries as Followit AB and Heden Group AB. Followit AB offer tracking solutions for wildlife and livestock animals, while Heden Group AB is specialized on lens motors and control systems for focus, iris and zoom control, which are in use for motion picture media industry.
